    "en": {
      "title": "The Sri Lankan squad is named for the Asian Cup",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sports Minister Mr. Roshan Ranasinghe has given approval to the Sri Lankan cricket squad participating in the Asian Cup cricket tournament. 20 players will be included in this squad led by Dasun Shanaka and vice-captain Charith Sasanka.",
        "Young player Dunil Vellalage did not have a place in this squad, but rookie players Dilshan Madhushanka and Nuvanindu Fernando have been included in this squad.",
        "Sri Lanka Squad - Dasun Shanaka (captain), Charith Asanka (vice-captain), Dhanushka Gunathilake, Pathum Nishanka, Kusal Mendis (wicketkeeper), Bhanuka Rajapaksa (wicketkeeper), Dinesh Chandimal (wicketkeeper), Ashen Bandara, Dhananjaya de Silva, Vanindu Hasaranga, Mahish Theekshana, Geoffrey Wandase, Praveen Jayawickrama, Dushmantha Chamira, Binura Fernando, Chamika Karunaratne, Dilshan Pathirana, Kasun Rajitha, Nuvanindu Fernando, Matisha Pathirana"
